weaknesses are, for example, a high computational demands for production
cloud free mosaics, inability to identify initial phases of forest
health decline, exclusion of stands older than 80 years (in the Czech
Republic) and inability to differentiate between harvested and severely
damaged stands (in Slovakia). Finally, the paper outlines future
development of both methodologies.},
